node.text: I asked some of my athlete friends, who are also trying to stay fit, to join me on my mixed relay team 😈🤜🏼🤛🏼 Enjoi everyone’s tricks, then show us some of yours! What are you guys doing to stay fit? // Thanks  @robin_haase @daniellevddonk @mennovangorp @nienkevanoverveld @femheemskerk @douwemacare @esther_fokke @adrienraza @dylan_vork @frederiquematla @rooszwettie // #teamfit #fittogether

node.text:
@sls Salt Lake City was a good one! I took my first SLS podium, something I dreamed of when I started skateboarding as a little kid 👶🏼 Thanks for all the support and messages, really appreciate it! 

See you in Miami! 

Congrats @rayssalealsk8 🥇 and @funa_nakayama 🥈and congrats to all the other skaters that competed!
📸: @inshanephotos

node.text:
What a day, what a day! The first Female Olympic Skateboarding competition was one to remember 🙌🏼

Thanks everyone for all the sweet messages and support, I really appreciate it!! 🤍 Unfortunately, not all my tricks worked out the way I wanted but still proud of my 5th place in the finals here at The Olympics. 

BIG thumps up to all the other girls out there that competed. Special congrats to @momiji_nishiya830 🥇 @rayssalealsk8 🥈 @funa_nakayama 🥉

node.text: Unfortunately I couldn’t skate the finals today because of a foot injury.. Still had a lot of fun this week, thank you Rome 🇮🇹✌🏼 Will be back on the board asap! See you in Tokyo! 🇯🇵 // Filmed by: @s.vlemmings @k.blewanus

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by R O O S   ☡ W E T S L O O T on May 24, 2021 tagging @dewtour, @pamelarosaskt, and @rayssalealsk8. May be an image of 3 people and outdoors.

node.text:
What a day yesterday! So happy to wear the Dutch flag on my first podium on a international competition 🇳🇱 Very proud of @keetoldenbeuving for making it to the finals, taking the 6th place and ensuring a ticket to Tokyo 🧡 Special thanks to @s.vlemmings @hansdanielvandorssen and @k.blewanus for all the support! 

Congrats to @pamelarosaskt and @rayssalealsk8 for absolutely smashing it and taking the 1st and 2nd place 🏆 Thank you @dewtour and @worldskateofficial for organising this event! Now on to the next one, Rome World Championships // Shots By: @unprvlgd.prod
